            ğŸ‘¤ Kunden
          </a>
          <a href="https://crm.synclaro.de/crm/transcripts" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 hover:border-swiss-orange hover:text-swiss-orange transition-colors text-sm">
            ğŸ“ Transkripte
          </a>
          <a href="https://app.netlify.com/teams/quualle/overview" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 hover:border-swiss-orange hover:text-swiss-orange transition-colors text-sm">
            ğŸš€ Netlify
