          <a href="https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/ouqhysemcldamthpuqqq" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 hover:border-swiss-orange hover:text-swiss-orange transition-colors text-sm">
            ğŸ—„ï¸ Supabase
